As a user, I want to create and edit my profile, so that I can personalize my account with a username, profile picture, biography and status.
As a user, I want to configure privacy settings in my profile, so that I can control who sees my posts and profile details; my family, friends, followers or everyone.

As a user, I want to create a post with a minimum length of 1 word, so that I can quickly share my thoughts and feelings.
As a user, I want to preview my post before publishing, so that I can ensure it looks as I intended and how it will be shown to my public. 

As a user, I want to view posts from other users in my feed, so that I can stay updated on what others are sharing.
As a user, I want to like posts from other users, so that I can raise the self-esteem of the people I follow.
As a user, I want to comment on posts, so that I can show feedback and share my thoughts on their content.
As a user, I want to tag other users in my posts and comments, so that I can involve them in conversations or content.

As a user, I want to include photos and videos in my posts, so that I can show what I'm doing.
As a user, I want to include links in my posts, so that I can redirect my audience to a publication of interest. 
As a user, I want to be able to reply to posts with my own posts, so that I can began a trend.

As a user, I want to search for posts using hashtags, so that I can find content related to specific topics of interest.
As a user, I want to view the most used hashtags of the day, so that I can discover trending topics and join them to increase my followers.
